Module com.alike
Package com.alike.solution_helpers

Class AtomicDouble

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
com.alike.solution_helpers.AtomicDouble
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<AtomicDouble>
public class AtomicDouble extends Number implements Comparable<AtomicDouble>
Class used to allow Ant threads to manipulate doubles in the pheromone and probabilty matrices without concurrency issues.
